bove approx. 83% of the Operational Capacity of 2,443,716 Dth - approx. 2,028,284 Dth.<br/><br/>The Operational Capacity of the Milwaukee Lateral (Location 505621) will be controlled to 500,000 Dth when the total nominations for Wisconsin (Location 261194)/Sandwich Northbound (Location FPSNDWNB) are below approx. 83% of the Operational Capacity of 2,443,716 Dth - approx. 2,028,284 Dth.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">ANR will implement these changes effective for gas day 11/1/2025 and will continue to evaluate operating conditions and market demands. This information is subject to change and will be updated as needed.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Please direct any questions to your Account Coordinator, Customer Service Representative, or the Nominations and Scheduling hotline @ 800-827-5267&#160;</span></DIV></DIV></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></TD><TD WIDTH=\\\"100%\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"0\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH=\\\"0\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"100%\\\"></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></DIV></body></html>\"},\"startTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:13:32.7039111Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:13:32.7834964Z\",\"trackingId\":\"886a3727-1678-490b-a375-3346acef69ea\",\"clientTrackingId\":\"08584249018052146792210398495CU00\",\"code\":\"OK\",\"status\":\"Succeeded\"},{\"name\":\"Call_Foundry_Extraction\",\"inputs\":{\"uri\":\"https://cog-dte-noticeapp-eus2-mx01.cognitiveservices.azure.com//openai/deployments/gpt-5.2/chat/completions?api-version=2024-02-01\",\"method\":\"POST\",\"body\":{\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"system\",\"content\":\"You are a structured data extraction assistant. Extract information from HTML documents and return only valid JSON. Be precise and thorough.\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Extract the