\\\" LANG=\\\"en-US\\\" style=\\\"\\\"><TR><TD style=\\\"WIDTH:195.11mm;min-width: 195.11mm;HEIGHT:6.35mm;\\\" class=\\\"a54 r8\\\"><DIV style=\\\"overflow-x:hidden;WIDTH:193.70mm;\\\"><DIV style=\\\"margin-top:10pt;padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Notice to All ANR Wisconsin Area (Zone 7) Shippers and Producers, Effective 11/1/25 – 3/31/26</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">&#160;</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">ANR continues to evaluate Wisconsin Winter Operations and Constraint Areas to both protect system integrity and provide customer flexibility.<br/><br/>Based on operational conditions and market demands, ANR is providing the following update regarding the Operational Capacity of the Milwaukee Lateral Constraint Group.<br/><br/>The Operational Capacity of the Milwaukee Lateral (Location 505621) will be controlled to 459,051 Dth when the total nominations for Wisconsin (Location 261194)/Sandwich Northbound (Location FPSNDWNB) are at or above approx. 83% of the Operational Capacity of 2,443,716 Dth - approx. 2,028,284 Dth.<br/><br/>The Operational Capacity of the Milwaukee Lateral (Location 505621) will be controlled to 500,000 Dth when the total nominations for Wisconsin (Location 261194)/Sandwich Northbound (Location FPSNDWNB) are below approx. 83% of the Operational Capacity of 2,443,716 Dth - approx. 2,028,284 Dth.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">ANR will implement these changes effective for gas day 11/1/2025 and will continue to evaluate operating conditions and market demands. This information is subject to change and will be updated as needed.</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'\\\"calibri\\\",sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Please direct any questions to your Account Coordinator, Customer Service Representative, or the Nominations and Scheduling hotline @ 800-827-5267&#160;</span></DIV></DIV></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></TD><TD WIDTH=\\\"100%\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"0\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH=\\\"0\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"100%\\\"></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></DIV></body></html>\"}],\"temperature\":0.1,\"max_tokens\":2000,\"response_format\":{\"type\":\"json_object\"}},\"headers\":{\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\",\"api-key\":\"AwX1mym8WNOwDFipRpDFxrz1bvaIAZJFkHH126iCClxlMtQOH5GUJQQJ99CDACHYHv6XJ3w3AAAAACOGUqcL\"}},\"outputs\":{\"statusCode\":400,\"headers\":{\"x-ms-rai-invoked\":\"true\",\"X-Request-ID\":\"8272a350-a2a5-4c96-a161-7f6e33adf30b\",\"apim-request-id\":\"803a5bb6-a48a-492d-ad82-01f11bf6a164\",\"Strict-Transport-Security\":\"max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains; preload\",\"x-ms-client-request-id\":\"468aad03-dfde-4a13-b441-d53ee72f2ab5\",\"x-ms-deployment-name\":\"gpt-5.2\",\"X-Content-Type-Options\":\"nosniff\",\"x-ms-region\":\"East US 2\",\"Date\":\"Mon, 20 Apr 2026 17:13:32 GMT\",\"Content-Length\":\"245\",\"Content-Type\":\"application/json\"},\"body\":{\"error\":{\"message\":\"Unsupported parameter: 'max_tokens' is not supported with this model. Use 'max_completion_tokens' instead.\",\"type\":\"invalid_request_error\",\"param\":\"max_tokens\",\"code\":\"unsupported_parameter\"}}},\"startTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:13:32.7937938Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:13:32.8539576Z\",\"trackingId\":\"e18d201a-0157-45f4-9d51-b66726940317\",\"clientTrackingId\":\"08584249018052146792210398495CU00\",\"code\":\"BadRequest\",\"status\":\"Failed\"},{\"name\":\"Parse_Foundry_Response\",\"startTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:13:32.8628236Z\",\"endTime\":\"2026-04-20T17:13:32.8635884Z\",\"trac